# HKMetadataKeyVO2MaxTestType

**Global Variable**

The method used to calculate the user’s VO2 max rate.

## Declaration

```swift
let HKMetadataKeyVO2MaxTestType: String
```

## Discussion

This key takes an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber] object containing a [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKVO2MaxTestType] value.

## Valid Test Types

- **HKVO2MaxTestType**: Methods for calculating the user’s VO2 max rate.
